    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/62c393433b87e7ad6352a646bcc6311b.avif?t=1732099105\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>监督官们刚刚收到了一批新武器，其中就包括哈兹克.50雷帽式步枪、M1伊万尼克和米勒1891步枪这类顶级狩猎武器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >哈兹克.50雷帽式步枪：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/dc6853abb798e1ccb07f2285d6e87391.poster.avif?t=1732099105\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/dc6853abb798e1ccb07f2285d6e87391.webm?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/dc6853abb798e1ccb07f2285d6e87391.mp4?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>造型优雅精致的哈兹克是内战时代的高端雷帽式步枪。这款前膛枪保养得近乎完美，时至今日它仍然可以满足传统猎人在狩猎中的多方位需求，前提是他们能够适应它那复杂且耗时的装弹操作。对于资深猎人来说，哈兹克是一款无可挑剔的武器，它正印证了那句俗话——“挑战越大，回报越大”。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><strong>3种颜色选择： </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/5a312a1d186c7392292b767cb9eed73b.poster.avif?t=1732099105\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/5a312a1d186c7392292b767cb9eed73b.webm?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/5a312a1d186c7392292b767cb9eed73b.mp4?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>哈兹克.50雷帽式步枪共有3种颜色选择：大地、皓月和曜日<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M1伊万尼克：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/13e5927e021851a9a9d1513a77c38a98.poster.avif?t=1732099105\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/13e5927e021851a9a9d1513a77c38a98.webm?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/13e5927e021851a9a9d1513a77c38a98.mp4?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>M1伊万尼克是一款战时英雄的标配步枪，每次击发，它的弹匣就会发出标志性的“乒”的一声。它凭借稳定的表现、均衡的性能和半自动击发的特性成为了全能型枪械中的佼佼者，这也一点得到了士兵、射击爱好者和猎人的充分认同。唯一需要注意的是，装弹的时候不要夹到大拇指！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><strong>3种颜色选择：</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/55550c243635dfbb76e1a512572f5227.poster.avif?t=1732099105\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/55550c243635dfbb76e1a512572f5227.webm?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/55550c243635dfbb76e1a512572f5227.mp4?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>M1伊万尼克共有3种颜色选择：老兵、预备役和佣兵<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >米勒1891步枪：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/a0025ae5cc2ce2f6182410ba89581c4f.poster.avif?t=1732099105\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/a0025ae5cc2ce2f6182410ba89581c4f.webm?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/a0025ae5cc2ce2f6182410ba89581c4f.mp4?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>米勒1891步枪是一款经久耐用的武器，这款杠杆式霰弹枪可以通过发射10铅径的黄铜子弹输出巨量伤害，向那款当年征服了西部的枪械致敬。米勒1891步枪的口径尺寸冠绝市面上的所有霰弹枪，它绝对是终结近距离战斗的大杀器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><strong>3种颜色选择：</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/425677b54f7d1e0b577f799ccc071983.poster.avif?t=1732099105\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/425677b54f7d1e0b577f799ccc071983.webm?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1252750/extras/425677b54f7d1e0b577f799ccc071983.mp4?t=1732099105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>米勒1891步枪共有3种颜色选择：农场主、副警长和治安官",
